    /**
     * A {@link Gtk.ListBoxRow} that looks like a button.
     * 
     * <picture>
     *   <source srcset="https://gnome.pages.gitlab.gnome.org/libadwaita/doc/1-latest/button-rows-dark.png" media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)">
     *   <img src="https://gnome.pages.gitlab.gnome.org/libadwaita/doc/1-latest/button-rows.png" alt="button-rows">
     * </picture>
     * 
     * The {@link Adw.ButtonRow} widget has a title and two icons: before and after the
     * title.
     * 
     * It is convenient for presenting actions like "Delete" at the end of a boxed
     * list.
     * 
     * {@link Adw.ButtonRow} is always activatable.
     * 
     * ## CSS nodes
     * 
     * {@link Adw.ButtonRow} has a main CSS node with name `row` and the style class
     * `.button`.
     * 
     * It contains the subnode `box` for its main horizontal box, which contains the
     * nodes: `image.icon.start` for the start icon, `label.title` for the title,
     * and `image.icon.end` for the end icon.
     * 
     * ## Style classes
     * 
     * The [`.suggested-action`](https://gnome.pages.gitlab.gnome.org/libadwaita/doc/1-latest/style-classes.html#suggested-action) style class
     * makes {@link Adw.ButtonRow} use accent color for its background. It should be used
     * very sparingly to denote important buttons.
     * 
     * <picture>
     *   <source srcset="https://gnome.pages.gitlab.gnome.org/libadwaita/doc/1-latest/button-row-suggested-action-dark.png" media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)">
     *   <img src="https://gnome.pages.gitlab.gnome.org/libadwaita/doc/1-latest/button-row-suggested-action.png" alt="button-row-suggested-action">
     * </picture>
     * 
     * The [`.destructive-action`](https://gnome.pages.gitlab.gnome.org/libadwaita/doc/1-latest/style-classes.html#destructive-action) style
     * makes the row use destructive colors. It can be used to draw attention to the
     * potentially damaging consequences of using it. This style acts as a warning
     * to the user.
     * 
     * <picture>
     *   <source srcset="https://gnome.pages.gitlab.gnome.org/libadwaita/doc/1-latest/button-row-destructive-action-dark.png" media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)">
     *   <img src="https://gnome.pages.gitlab.gnome.org/libadwaita/doc/1-latest/button-row-destructive-action.png" alt="button-row-destructive-action">
     * </picture>
     * @gir-type Class
     * @since 1.6
     */
